Truck drivers in Victoria are dealing drugs from the 60-tonne rigs , using secretive codes over their radio systems .
In a report , Victoria police revealed that there is a distribution network of speed , ice and marijuana operating in the trucking industry and one in every 12 truckies tested positive for drugs while out on the road .
